Message: The user completes the submission of the form
Hey Boss please help me to setup web events. I am Using Bmob as a tracker.

Sure thing! I can help you set up web events using BeMob as your tracker. Here are the steps you need to follow:
1. Log into your NewsBreak account and head to Event Management, then click 'Create/Test Web Event.'
2. Select the Event Type and whether or not you want to pass a value back.
3. Copy this Postback URL for NewsBreak: `https://business.newsbreak.com/tracking/attribute?callback=xxx&event_type=complete_registration&nb_value=xxx`
4. Switch tabs to BeMob and create a new traffic channel for NewsBreak (if not created already) and use the following details for the template:
   - The Parameter needs to be populated by our click id macro i.e., `__CALLBACK_PARAM__`.
   - Double-check that your Postback URL is filled in with the correct endpoint.
5. Click 'Save' and head to Campaigns to create a new campaign.
6. Select NewsBreak as your traffic source, fill in the Offer details (selecting the Offer), and hit Save.
7. Head to the newly created campaign and hit the â€˜Actionsâ€™ button.
8. When the dropdown populates, click 'Copy URL.' This would copy the Campaign URL which should look something like this: `https://click.bestautoinsuranceclub.com/go/7e6c17f6-c030-4000-b3bb-079d4263971e?CALLBACK_PARAM=__CALLBACK_PARAM__&__CAMPAIGN_ID__=__CAMPAIGN_ID__&__CAMPAIGN_NAME__=__CAMPAIGN_NAME__&__FLIGHT_ID__=__FLIGHT_ID__&__FLIGHT_NAME__=__FLIGHT_NAME__&__CREATIVE_ID__=__CREATIVE_ID__& __CREATIVE_NAME __ = __ CREATIVE_NAME __ & __ OS __ = __ OS __`
9. Switch back to NewsBreak's Event Management tab and enter this URL in the Test URL field.
10. Hit â€˜Go Testâ€™ and you should be redirected to the Offer landing page, where you need to follow the steps to complete the conversion (In this case, complete a registration form).
11. Once you complete the conversion event on this landing page, we should receive a success message from BeMob, completing the Event Testing.
For more detailed instructions, please refer to this article: [How-to-setup-a-Newsbreak-Postback-on-BeMob](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/30938725150733-How-to-setup-a-Newsbreak-Postback-on-BeMob).
Connecting you to a live agent. Please hold.
